        </div>

        <div class="slide active">
          <div class="slide-content markdown">
            <script type="text/markdown">
            # Key Takeaways

            - Computational complexity predicts scalability
            - Time and space both matter
            - Big-O compares growth, not exact speed
            - Choose algorithms that scale well

            Good complexity = happy users!

            </script>
          </div>
        </div>
        
